HEADWORD: Solo whist
<hw>Solo whist</hw>. <def>A card game played with the full pack ranking
as at whist, each player declaring for which of seven different points
he proposes to play.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

